{"tid":1709963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲覺得區選有用果班其實係咪卡咗係時空裂縫？","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T04:55:22.000Z","uid":64181,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe43b2103d8591d02699f01837d6ec7549dacb2","tid":1709963,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"03年大遊行，之後果屆區選大勝，一班政治新人當選成名，但到今日果班人有d變建制有d變關鍵時刻柒嘅左膠。而係大局方面，香港人以為香港係民主勝利，之後個個都受自由行 cepa果d 毒害香港政策<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/162455_b95b23fb4ab68670a4733f7d69d7a701.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F162455_b95b23fb4ab68670a4733f7d69d7a701.png&h=912f7af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14年雨革後，又一次區選大勝，但果班上位新人到依家可能都叫唔出名。而係大局方面，愈來愈近2047大限，加上貿易戰，中共對香港再落重藥借台灣殺人案推出逃犯修訂條例<br />\n<br />\n我想問兩次區選大勝，想問香港係咪已經係果陣贏撚咗？成日問點解香港搞成咁，但到叫你做野果陣就投票就得，食屎果陣就問點解我要慘到食屎，叫你做d野唔好再食屎又話自己廢，投票當有幫手，我屌你啦，孫中山當年一定係投票投撚死清朝啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>血債只有血償，屌你老母港豬</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"971ed62b2fd6a3a2cf55213f73ca8b44e3cfa885","tid":1709963,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">出門前入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n入 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/task</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=7c73119a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n有Telegram的人請加入<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Twitter共識Channel</span><br />\ntwitter組每日會更新主線副線任務<br />\n方便大家知道每日有咩議員外媒國際大事<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + 響原Tweet reply</span><br />